  "description": {
    "zh": "嗨！你还记得那个和Reshala做过生意的人吗？就是上次我们给过一批好货的人。看起来他现在已经有了高档生活的品味，想要搞一些古董花瓶和古董茶壶。我可以理解他想要几只古董花瓶，但是他为什么还想要什么狗屁古董茶壶呢？算了，不管他，生意就是生意，他开的价够高就行。所有货物必须是全新的，所以你需要亲自去找。",
    "en": "Hey. Do you remember the guy who had some business with Reshala? The one we gave the goodies last time. Yeah, so looks like he's got a taste of the luxury lifestyle now, he wants some antique vases and antique teapots, I understand it with the vases, but why the hell could he possibly need so many antique teapots? Anyway, a deal is a deal, he pays well for it. Everything has to be fresh and untouched, so find them yourself."
  },
